October 2001
Top level directory for the "wurst" code.

Directories
-----------
matrix
This holds amino acid substitution matrices.

pod
This is documentation.

scripts
Perl / wurst scripts

scripts/optim_seq
Scripts for optimising parameters for alignment.

seq
Sequences - do not start putting sequences, even for testing,
in places like src.

src
Source code. Within src, there is...

src/Wurst
which holds the perl extension code, the module file, and the
interface files.

src/Simplex
Module for simplex optimisation.

struct
Structures. Real structures live in other places, so this is
for debugging coordinates.